relevant_findings.general: Pleasant, well-appearing, in no apparent distress.
relevant_findings.heent: Normocephalic, atraumatic, no conjunctival pallor or scleral icterus, PERRLA, EOMI, OP clear.
relevant_findings.neck: Supple, no LAD, no thyromegaly, JVP flat.
relevant_findings.cardiac: RRR, normal S1/S2, systolic murmur heard throughout precordium, loudest at RUSB.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, without wheezes or rhonchi.
relevant_findings.abdomen: Normal bowel sounds, soft. Tender throughout, most in epigastrium then RUQ. No r/g.
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well-perfused, no cyanosis, clubbing or edema.
relevant_findings.skin: Chronic venous stasis changes of b/l extremities.
